WEBVTT

00:01:23.439 --> 00:01:24.239
Young Master

00:01:24.359 --> 00:01:25.560
Everything is arranged.

00:01:25.599 --> 00:01:26.439
It's foolproof.

00:01:26.840 --> 00:01:27.959
The border situation has changed.

00:01:28.079 --> 00:01:29.120
Stabilizing the rear

00:01:29.120 --> 00:01:30.079
admits no delay.

00:01:30.599 --> 00:01:31.400
Perfect.

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:34.200
I want to help Qingqiu save the Leng Family.

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:36.079
Mr. Gu.

00:01:36.159 --> 00:01:37.200
The Chairman invites you in.

00:01:37.560 --> 00:01:38.400
Please.

00:01:43.159 --> 00:01:43.959
After you.

00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:52.760
Why is Lu Chengwen here?

00:01:53.239 --> 00:01:55.000
If you're setting me up,

00:01:55.200 --> 00:01:56.400
I'll kill you.

00:01:56.640 --> 00:01:58.079
Feel free to show off your charm.

00:01:58.200 --> 00:01:59.680
I'll help you get back on track.

00:02:00.400 --> 00:02:01.560
Mr. Gu, right?

00:02:02.400 --> 00:02:04.400
For the sake of my future son-in-law,

00:02:04.799 --> 00:02:06.239
I'll give you 30 seconds.

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:07.560
President Leng.

00:02:08.800 --> 00:02:10.840
Haicheng will build an

00:02:10.840 --> 00:02:12.800
Amusement City costing 30 billion.

00:02:13.080 --> 00:02:14.080
This news...

00:02:14.080 --> 00:02:15.560
You know about it, right?

00:02:18.360 --> 00:02:19.639
You have 20 seconds left.

00:02:22.199 --> 00:02:23.879
Gu Zhantian is about to show off.

00:02:24.240 --> 00:02:26.159
In a satisfying novel, a hype man is usually needed at this point.

00:02:26.840 --> 00:02:28.199
Green leaves to complement the flowers.

00:02:28.199 --> 00:02:28.960
Leave it to me.

00:02:29.479 --> 00:02:31.400
I can use two billion

00:02:31.400 --> 00:02:32.800
to secure the land in advance.

00:02:33.560 --> 00:02:34.360
No.

00:02:35.879 --> 00:02:37.000
It's us.

00:02:37.759 --> 00:02:38.599
Two billion?

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:41.599
The starting price for that land was four billion.

00:02:41.759 --> 00:02:43.400
Now he can get it for two billion.

00:02:43.759 --> 00:02:45.199
The resources he can mobilize behind the scenes...

00:02:45.199 --> 00:02:46.560
Unimaginable.

00:02:51.800 --> 00:02:52.360
Mr. Gu.

00:02:52.360 --> 00:02:52.639
Come.

00:02:52.639 --> 00:02:53.439
Please, have a seat.

00:02:53.439 --> 00:02:54.560
Regarding this matter,

00:02:54.800 --> 00:02:56.280
please explain it in detail.

00:02:57.039 --> 00:02:57.960
Great hype.

00:02:58.280 --> 00:03:00.479
We can use the two-billion land as shares.

00:03:00.800 --> 00:03:02.439
Once the Amusement City is built,

00:03:02.840 --> 00:03:04.199
our annual dividends

00:03:04.199 --> 00:03:05.759
can reach one billion.

00:03:07.240 --> 00:03:08.360
With such a huge investment,

00:03:08.400 --> 00:03:09.599
we can break even in two years.

00:03:09.800 --> 00:03:10.360
A business like this,

00:03:10.360 --> 00:03:11.400
let alone in Haicheng,

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:12.960
is hard to find anywhere else in the country.

00:03:13.560 --> 00:03:14.560
It won't take two years.

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:16.240
One year is enough.

00:03:16.280 --> 00:03:17.960
We can contract the construction project.

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:19.039
By then,

00:03:19.039 --> 00:03:21.199
it can bring profits in the early stage.

00:03:21.560 --> 00:03:22.360
One year?

00:03:23.039 --> 00:03:24.240
These builders in Haicheng

00:03:24.240 --> 00:03:25.960
are somewhat tied to local factions.

00:03:26.199 --> 00:03:28.039
For him to swallow such a big piece of meat,

00:03:28.400 --> 00:03:30.639
could he have already incorporated those factions?

00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:31.800
In this way,

00:03:31.960 --> 00:03:34.080
our Leng Family will be completely revived.

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:35.759
No more predicaments.

00:03:36.080 --> 00:03:37.039
Hahaha.

00:03:37.599 --> 00:03:39.800
Why is there such a comfortable rhythm?

00:03:40.240 --> 00:03:41.039
Strange.

00:03:41.599 --> 00:03:43.599
I'll help you win over this Leng Tianhao first.

00:03:44.280 --> 00:03:45.479
Once you pass his test,

00:03:45.479 --> 00:03:46.479
you can continue

00:03:46.479 --> 00:03:48.479
your romantic route with your Qingqiu.

00:03:48.599 --> 00:03:49.599
Then I'll be at ease.

00:04:00.039 --> 00:04:00.840
Darn it.

00:04:00.840 --> 00:04:01.759
I got carried away.

00:04:01.879 --> 00:04:03.400
I forgot to mute my phone.

00:04:03.840 --> 00:04:05.319
This project

00:04:05.319 --> 00:04:07.039
can indeed revive our Leng Family.

00:04:07.039 --> 00:04:08.280
But I have a question.

00:04:08.800 --> 00:04:09.599
Mr. Gu,

00:04:09.879 --> 00:04:11.439
what do you want out of this?

00:04:11.639 --> 00:04:12.439
Qingqiu,

00:04:13.039 --> 00:04:14.120
I'm doing all this

00:04:14.120 --> 00:04:15.280
just for you.

00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:16.079
I know

00:04:16.079 --> 00:04:18.480
revitalizing Qianfeng has always been your dream.

00:04:18.560 --> 00:04:20.000
I brought this news today

00:04:20.040 --> 00:04:21.959
hoping to help you save the Leng Family.

00:04:22.759 --> 00:04:23.759
I hope you

00:04:23.759 --> 00:04:25.240
won't jump into a fire pit.

00:04:25.800 --> 00:04:26.600
A fire pit?

00:04:30.439 --> 00:04:31.240
How dare you!

00:04:31.399 --> 00:04:32.720
Don't think just because you stumbled upon

00:04:32.720 --> 00:04:33.680
a profitable deal,

00:04:33.680 --> 00:04:35.639
you can belittle me.

00:04:35.959 --> 00:04:37.680
I have plenty of

00:04:37.680 --> 00:04:38.480
business deals here.

00:04:38.759 --> 00:04:39.560
Chengwen,

00:04:39.800 --> 00:04:41.360
what projects do you have?

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:44.839
This old fox wants a bite of every dish.

00:04:45.439 --> 00:04:47.439
Then I'll let you taste a spoiled one.

00:04:49.040 --> 00:04:51.399
I have a large-scale project here.

00:04:51.959 --> 00:04:54.800
The old town construction project in the south.

00:04:55.160 --> 00:04:56.240
The south city project?

00:04:56.240 --> 00:04:57.560
It takes a long time,

00:04:57.560 --> 00:04:58.040
requires huge investment,

00:04:58.040 --> 00:04:58.839
and has low profit.

00:04:59.199 --> 00:05:00.600
If that's not a fire pit, what is?

00:05:01.160 --> 00:05:01.959
Chengwen,

00:05:02.079 --> 00:05:03.680
the Lu family's funds

00:05:03.680 --> 00:05:05.680
can't withstand such a drain, right?

00:05:07.160 --> 00:05:07.959
Lu Chengwen,

00:05:08.160 --> 00:05:09.439
are you putting on this act

00:05:09.439 --> 00:05:11.040
just to avoid me?

00:05:11.560 --> 00:05:13.600
Don't you understand my feelings?

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:14.800
Dad,

00:05:15.199 --> 00:05:16.959
I think Brother Chengwen makes sense.

00:05:17.160 --> 00:05:18.079
I plan to

00:05:18.079 --> 00:05:20.160
co-invest in Brother Chengwen's south city project.

00:05:21.480 --> 00:05:22.120
What?

00:05:22.120 --> 00:05:23.600
Did it backfire?

00:05:23.800 --> 00:05:24.600
Qingqiu,

00:05:25.160 --> 00:05:27.000
the south city project is very complicated.

00:05:27.600 --> 00:05:28.199
Besides,

00:05:28.199 --> 00:05:29.959
you know nothing about the infrastructure industry.

00:05:30.199 --> 00:05:31.759
Do I need to know that much?

00:05:32.240 --> 00:05:33.800
Isn't it enough that Brother Chengwen knows?

00:05:33.879 --> 00:05:34.680
Nonsense!

00:05:35.040 --> 00:05:36.399
Who doesn't know that's a trap?

00:05:37.199 --> 00:05:38.040
I disagree.

00:05:38.199 --> 00:05:38.800
Dad,

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:40.680
you were the one who told me to marry into the Lu family.

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:42.480
You also told me yourself

00:05:42.680 --> 00:05:43.839
that the survival of the enterprise

00:05:44.079 --> 00:05:45.240
and the rise and fall of the family

00:05:45.959 --> 00:05:48.160
are more important than my personal happiness.

00:05:48.399 --> 00:05:49.879
I have a marriage contract with Brother Chengwen.

00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:51.560
He is my future husband.

00:05:51.759 --> 00:05:53.560
So I trust him unconditionally.

00:05:53.879 --> 00:05:54.839
Is there a problem?

00:05:54.959 --> 00:05:56.240
Why do you disagree?

00:05:56.399 --> 00:05:57.759
You useless thing!

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:00.600
Dad,

00:06:01.680 --> 00:06:03.759
over the years,

00:06:03.759 --> 00:06:05.399
I've made our Qianfeng Group

00:06:05.560 --> 00:06:07.639
one of the largest enterprises in Haicheng.

00:06:08.160 --> 00:06:10.040
But the moment I displease you slightly,

00:06:10.839 --> 00:06:12.240
I become a useless thing.

00:06:12.600 --> 00:06:14.000
Then I'll be willful just this once.

00:06:14.800 --> 00:06:16.600
I just want to trust Brother Chengwen.

00:06:16.639 --> 00:06:17.879
If he wants to trap me,

00:06:18.040 --> 00:06:19.160
I'll let him trap me.

00:06:19.959 --> 00:06:21.079
If he wants to harm me,

00:06:21.399 --> 00:06:22.560
I'll let him harm me.

00:06:23.480 --> 00:06:25.079
If he wants to sell me for money,

00:06:26.680 --> 00:06:29.000
then I'll set a good price for myself.

00:06:33.680 --> 00:06:34.399
This...

00:06:34.399 --> 00:06:37.279
How did this turn into a father-daughter drama?

00:06:38.160 --> 00:06:38.959
Lu Chengwen,

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:41.439
what exactly do you have on her

00:06:41.879 --> 00:06:44.040
to make her jump into your fire pit?

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:47.040
I'll go talk to her.

00:06:49.160 --> 00:06:49.959
President Leng,

00:06:50.600 --> 00:06:51.600
I'll take my leave.

00:06:56.800 --> 00:06:57.560
Lu Chengwen

00:06:58.360 --> 00:06:59.399
You still haven't given up.

00:06:59.399 --> 00:07:00.639
Still trying to trick Leng Qingqiu.

00:07:00.759 --> 00:07:02.839
Are you hoping that after the Leng Family completely falls,

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:04.399
you can acquire Qianfeng Group at a low price?

00:07:04.399 --> 00:07:06.560
By then, both Qianfeng Group and Leng Qingqiu

00:07:06.600 --> 00:07:08.399
will become your playthings.

00:07:08.439 --> 00:07:09.240
Am I right?

00:07:09.439 --> 00:07:10.240
No!

00:07:10.279 --> 00:07:10.680
It's a misunderstanding.

00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:11.480
Brother Zhantian.

00:07:11.560 --> 00:07:13.959
I brought up the Chengnan project to help you!

00:07:14.079 --> 00:07:16.040
Who knew Leng Qingqiu's stubborn temper would flare up

00:07:16.040 --> 00:07:17.160
and she'd act like this?

00:07:17.160 --> 00:07:18.079
Help me?

00:07:18.399 --> 00:07:19.399
What an insult to human nature.

00:07:20.439 --> 00:07:22.199
Villains here just exist to make you protagonists look good.

00:07:22.199 --> 00:07:24.160
That's the only way to show how brilliant you are.

00:07:30.560 --> 00:07:31.279
Anyway,

00:07:31.279 --> 00:07:33.000
I'll help you persuade Leng Qingqiu to come back.

00:07:33.160 --> 00:07:34.160
Let her cool down a bit.

00:07:34.199 --> 00:07:35.319
You just keep helping her invest in that

00:07:35.319 --> 00:07:36.439
Amusement City project.

00:07:38.800 --> 00:07:39.759
What novel?

00:07:39.879 --> 00:07:40.759
What protagonist?

00:07:41.399 --> 00:07:42.759
This man is full of tricks.

00:07:42.879 --> 00:07:44.360
I definitely can't let him live.

00:08:13.560 --> 00:08:14.360
It's...

00:08:15.560 --> 00:08:16.639
so cold.

00:08:17.879 --> 00:08:18.800
What are you doing?

00:08:19.160 --> 00:08:20.199
I'm so cold.

00:08:20.480 --> 00:08:21.800
If you're not cold,

00:08:22.000 --> 00:08:24.000
lend me your clothes.

00:08:27.040 --> 00:08:28.199
Are you crazy?

00:08:30.800 --> 00:08:31.680
Leng Qingqiu.

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:33.240
Your name...

00:08:33.240 --> 00:08:34.279
sounds cold just hearing it.

00:08:34.440 --> 00:08:36.440
Plus, you're an iceberg beauty.

00:08:37.159 --> 00:08:38.480
Sitting next to you,

00:08:38.559 --> 00:08:39.639
and when you get mad,

00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:42.559
it's like falling into an Antarctic iceberg.

00:08:46.399 --> 00:08:47.240
The ice has melted.

00:08:48.559 --> 00:08:49.440
You're never serious.

00:08:52.440 --> 00:08:53.200
Lu Chengwen,

00:08:53.960 --> 00:08:55.960
do you think the South City project can make money?

00:08:56.080 --> 00:08:56.879
To be honest,

00:08:58.600 --> 00:09:01.360
only someone out of their mind would invest in that project.

00:09:02.879 --> 00:09:04.559
Then why did you sound so confident?

00:09:04.799 --> 00:09:06.759
How was I supposed to know you'd actually invest?

00:09:08.840 --> 00:09:10.279
I didn't expect it either.

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:11.399
It was just a moment of...

00:09:11.399 --> 00:09:12.639
getting emotional.

00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:16.480
You were pissed off by your dad.

00:09:18.200 --> 00:09:19.559
I wasn't really angry.

00:09:20.080 --> 00:09:21.799
I was just very disappointed in my dad.

00:09:26.080 --> 00:09:27.399
When I have some free time,

00:09:27.399 --> 00:09:28.000
I'll help you

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:29.000
teach him a lesson.

00:09:32.159 --> 00:09:34.039
I used to admire him a lot when I was little,

00:09:34.039 --> 00:09:35.600
and I always learned from him.

00:09:35.960 --> 00:09:38.000
But he never praised me.

00:09:38.440 --> 00:09:39.759
Later, I finally understood

00:09:40.360 --> 00:09:42.360
that Qianfeng is his real child.

00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:44.360
I'm nothing but a tool.

00:09:46.559 --> 00:09:48.000
When I was in college,

00:09:48.279 --> 00:09:49.039
he arranged for me

00:09:49.039 --> 00:09:51.000
to meet the son of a shipping tycoon.

00:09:51.039 --> 00:09:52.360
I was young back then,

00:09:52.399 --> 00:09:53.879
so I accepted that man.

00:09:54.200 --> 00:09:55.240
But in the end,

00:09:55.240 --> 00:09:56.399
when I was ready to give my all

00:09:56.440 --> 00:09:57.879
to that man,

00:09:58.360 --> 00:09:59.320
I found out

00:09:59.320 --> 00:10:00.679
he actually wanted to secretly film me,

00:10:01.000 --> 00:10:02.399
and use those videos

00:10:02.399 --> 00:10:03.360
to blackmail me

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:04.559
and plot for my family's fortune.

00:10:06.360 --> 00:10:08.399
No wonder you hated me so much before.

00:10:12.279 --> 00:10:13.559
What kind of videos was he secretly filming?

00:10:15.440 --> 00:10:17.279
Well, if I were your dad,

00:10:17.559 --> 00:10:19.360
I'd pay someone

00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:20.440
to take him out.

00:10:21.759 --> 00:10:23.200
He called me an idiot

00:10:23.799 --> 00:10:25.559
for almost letting someone get leverage over me.

00:10:32.799 --> 00:10:33.600
It's okay.

00:10:33.840 --> 00:10:35.159
You don't need to worry about me.

00:10:35.559 --> 00:10:36.960
I'm very strong.

00:10:37.360 --> 00:10:39.159
I've already moved on.

00:10:45.080 --> 00:10:45.879
Lu Chengwen,

00:10:47.279 --> 00:10:48.759
take a walk with me.

00:10:54.480 --> 00:10:55.279
Qingqiu,

00:10:55.360 --> 00:10:56.200
I think

00:10:56.200 --> 00:10:57.879
the Amusement City project is really good.

00:10:57.879 --> 00:10:59.159
With Gu Zhantian's help,

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:00.200
I believe

00:11:00.200 --> 00:11:01.559
the Leng Family will soon

00:11:01.559 --> 00:11:02.840
be able to turn things around.

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:04.480
Since that project is so good,

00:11:04.759 --> 00:11:05.759
why don't you invest in it?

00:11:06.159 --> 00:11:07.320
I'm really planning to invest in

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:09.000
the South City construction project.

00:11:09.279 --> 00:11:10.279
I don't have any extra money

00:11:10.279 --> 00:11:11.440
to invest in anything else.

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:13.000
Are you really going to invest in that project?

00:11:13.559 --> 00:11:15.159
I thought you were just talking nonsense.

00:11:15.240 --> 00:11:16.360
Then I want to join you

00:11:16.360 --> 00:11:17.200
in investing in South City.

00:11:17.440 --> 00:11:18.240
Qingqiu,

00:11:19.000 --> 00:11:20.840
the South City project has huge risks.

00:11:20.840 --> 00:11:22.200
Our Lu Family can afford the loss,

00:11:22.200 --> 00:11:23.759
but your Leng Family can't afford it!

00:11:23.799 --> 00:11:24.600
I know.

00:11:24.759 --> 00:11:25.960
But I still want to join you.

00:11:26.279 --> 00:11:27.080
No,

00:11:27.600 --> 00:11:28.759
but why?

00:11:35.399 --> 00:11:36.360
I think I...

00:11:44.799 --> 00:11:45.960
I've fallen for you.

00:11:54.159 --> 00:11:56.080
Say that again.

00:11:56.080 --> 00:11:56.879
I said...

00:11:56.960 --> 00:11:57.559
I...

00:11:57.559 --> 00:11:59.039
have fallen for you.

00:12:02.440 --> 00:12:03.840
You've fal...

00:12:03.879 --> 00:12:04.879
fallen for me?

00:12:06.600 --> 00:12:07.399
I know...

00:12:07.639 --> 00:12:08.720
I used to be...

00:12:08.720 --> 00:12:09.639
very cold to you.

00:12:09.639 --> 00:12:10.440
And very annoyed.

00:12:10.799 --> 00:12:12.039
But as you know...

00:12:12.039 --> 00:12:12.960
I don't know why,

00:12:12.960 --> 00:12:14.360
but I can hear your inner thoughts.

00:12:14.799 --> 00:12:16.279
I realized you're a good person.

00:12:16.679 --> 00:12:18.799
Not the kind of good that gets friend-zoned.

00:12:19.000 --> 00:12:19.879
But...

00:12:19.879 --> 00:12:21.080
But...

00:12:21.799 --> 00:12:22.559
Anyway,

00:12:22.679 --> 00:12:23.759
if you're willing,

00:12:23.879 --> 00:12:24.759
starting from now,

00:12:24.759 --> 00:12:26.159
I am your girlfriend.

00:12:26.600 --> 00:12:27.600
As for the engagement,

00:12:27.759 --> 00:12:29.000
if you think it's too rushed,

00:12:29.159 --> 00:12:30.399
we can take it slow.

00:12:30.639 --> 00:12:32.000
We can start by just dating.

00:12:32.000 --> 00:12:32.639
And then...

00:12:33.000 --> 00:12:33.440
Brother Chengwen?

00:12:34.360 --> 00:12:35.440
Brother Chengwen?

00:12:35.440 --> 00:12:36.279
Brother Chengwen!

00:12:36.600 --> 00:12:38.080
Say something, Brother Chengwen!

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:42.559
Hello?

00:12:42.559 --> 00:12:43.360
Is this 120?

00:12:43.360 --> 00:12:44.679
Someone fainted here.

00:12:44.679 --> 00:12:46.200
I just confessed my feelings to him,

00:12:46.240 --> 00:12:47.480
and he suddenly collapsed.

00:12:47.679 --> 00:12:48.840
Like he just crashed.

00:12:49.879 --> 00:12:50.000
No,

00:12:50.000 --> 00:12:51.279
no need to contact a funeral home!

00:12:51.279 --> 00:12:52.960
Just send an ambulance quickly!

00:12:53.200 --> 00:12:54.000
Where?

